room_title: Escape room "Prison" by Amazing Escape in Atlanta
room_address: 6040 Unity Dr Suite C, Norcross, GA 30071
room_description: You and your crew are handcuffed in a holding cell, framed for a crime you did not commit. You have 45 minutes before you are moved to a maximum security prison. You are innocent, yet proven guilty. The only option is to escape!
